              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 6 <span style=\"color: #FFE699\">Geo DMG</span>. If <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Jade Screen</span> is on the field, deals +2 DMG.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Jade Screen</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Combat Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When your active character receives at least 2 DMG</span>: Decrease DMG taken by 1.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 2</span></p>",
